instruction:
To use vis, you must get the license key for it.
vis is free for private use, but for commercial use it has a price.
You can get the license on iobroker.net after short registration.
offline license has no serial number (UU: offline license has no serial number (UUID)
offline license must be linked to serial: offline license must be linked to serial number (UUID)
serial number (UUID) in license is for: serial number (UUID) in license is for other device
